snippet.title: Hawk F-123 (PC Engine CD)
snippet.description:
Since there were no videos for the gameplay on Hawk F-123, here's one humble contribution.
This video includes opening and brief scenes of all 8 stages. The ending sequence was sped up so that all cut scenes could be displayed.

Blog entry: http://1cclog.blogspot.com/2010/04/hawk-f-123-pc-engine-cd.html
